CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 21, 1956, pg. A1, reads: "Admiring Gifts - After their wedding at Ebenezer Baptist Church, Mr. and Mrs. Harry H. Griggs were 'caught' by the photographer as they admired their many lovely gifts. The bride is the former Vernetta D. Harris, 7211 Monticello St. - 'Teenie' Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Groom Harry H. Griggs wearing light colored dinner jacket, and bride Vernetta D. Harris Griggs wearing lace gown with high collar, posed in Ebenezer Baptist Church decorated with ferns and palms
